name: BronchiectasisI9
title: Bronchiectasis I9
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses most commonly used for patients with bronchiectasis.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have an active  diagnosis of bronchiectasis . Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes representing a diagnosis of bronchiectasis using the  ICD 9 CM code system.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
